&lt;p&gt;And our Movie Entity will look like:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;pre style="background-color: #ffffff; margin: 0em; width: 100%; font-family: consolas,'Courier New',courier,monospace; font-size: 12px"&gt;  1: &lt;span style="color: #0000ff"&gt;public&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color: #0000ff"&gt;class&lt;/span&gt; Movie : IMongoEntity
