&lt;p&gt;Notice I’m using JsonConverter to return a complex type, we should probably encapsulate that functionality in some kind of base class, maybe convert IMongoEntity into an abstract class that provides some basic utilities.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I will try to dig deeper into MongoDB, seems to be really suited to a Domain first approach. I wasn’t able to have anything but the most simple queries working, so I will have to take a closer look at the syntax.&lt;/p&gt;</Content>
